bilingual.source: Tomorrow we are camping by a river.
bilingual.target: 明天我们将在河边露营。

bilingual.source: We'll go camping and have a good time.
bilingual.target: 我们会去露营，玩得很开心。

bilingual.source: Mum, Dad and I went camping in Beidaihe.
bilingual.target: 妈妈、爸爸和我去了北戴河露营。

bilingual.source: We went camping in a small village in India.
bilingual.target: 我们在印度的一个小村庄露营。

bilingual.source: Miles and his dad were camping in the mountains.
bilingual.target: 迈尔斯和他的爸爸在山里露营。

bilingual.source: Visitors can enjoy many activities like camping.
bilingual.target: 游客可以享受许多活动，如露营。

bilingual.source: Make sure to keep dry while camping.

bilingual.target: 露营时，帐篷是必不可少的。

bilingual.source: A headlamp is very useful when camping.
A paraffin stove is great for camping.
bilingual.target: 煤油炉子很适合野外露营。

list.abstract: camping（露营）是一种休闲活动，通常离开城市在野外扎营，与徒步、钓鱼或者游泳等活动相联系。 camping基本可以分为三种形式，第一是常规露营，第二是汽车露营，第三种是特殊形式露营。露营所需装备通常有：帐篷、睡袋、背包、生火用具、照明用具、野炊用具等。

yingyinNormal.en: Your turn. I've never been on vacation. What about camping?
yingyinNormal.zh: 该你了。我没度过假。露营也没有过吗?

yingyinNormal.en: You've been camping before, haven't you? Well, never outside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你应该露营过，对吧? 其实，从没在户外。

yingyinNormal.en: Never mind, we are at the camp side now. Hooray. Happy camping, everyone. Bye-bye.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没关系，我们到露营地点啦。祝大家露营愉快啊！再见。

yingyinNormal.en: Kind of. What are you talking about? You invited her on that camping trip.
yingyinNormal.zh: 算是吧。你在说什么啊？你邀她参加露营。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. Daddy Pig, there is no point being on a camping holiday and just watching TV. We can do that at home.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，猪爸爸，如果你出来露营只是为了看电视的话，那我们的露营就没意义了。在家也能看电视。

yingyinNormal.en: I love camping. Since we are in the countryside, I thought we can spend the day looking at nature.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我喜欢露营。既然我们来到了郊外，我觉得我们可以去看看大自然的风景。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and her family are going camping. I love camping. We're here. Hurray!
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩琪一家人要去宿营啦。我最喜欢宿营啦。我们到啦。好嘞。

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy Pig! What? Daddy, you're safe! Of course I'm safe! I'm an expert at camping! I slept in the car. Silly Daddy! I love camping!
yingyinNormal.zh: 爸爸，你在这里呀！怎么了？爸爸，你没事吧 ！我当然不会有事了！我是宿营专家呀！我睡在车里面了。可怜的爸爸。我最喜欢宿营了！

yingyinNormal.en: He is really good at camping, and how to make fire from rocks and stuff.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他很擅长野营，会钻木取火。

yingyinNormal.en: I hate camping. If I'm ever in the woods for three days, it means I've been dead for two of them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我讨厌野营，我要是在丛林里待了三天，那意味着我已经死了两天了。

yingyinNormal.en: And that's more fun to you than going camping with your brother and your father who love you. Yes. Sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这样比跟你爸还有你弟去野营还有趣吗？我们那么爱你。是的，抱歉哦。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't worry, Peppa! I'm an expert at camping! Mummy Pig, put the tent on the poles, please. That's it! Easy as pie!
yingyinNormal.zh: 不用担心，佩琪，我是搭帐篷的好手。猪妈妈，请把布铺到柱子上。这样就行了，小菜一碟。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy Pig, Peppa and George are sleeping in the tent. Daddy Pig is sleeping outside, under the stars. I love camping!
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪妈妈，佩琪和乔治睡在帐篷里。猪爸爸在帐篷外的星空下睡着了。我真喜欢宿营 ！

yingyinNormal.en: What's very interesting is that sometimes for national games even standing in lines for a few days and camping out and coming to all the bills and the announcement is not enough.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很有意思的是有的时候，全国赛的门票不是你排几天队在外面露个营带上钞票和通知就能买到的。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: According to recent studies, the answer is a big YES, if the air quality in your <highlight>camping</highlight> area is good.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据最近的研究，答案是肯定的，如果你露营的地方空气质量好的话。

examination_example.sentence: You will be able to take part in a number of activities from canoeing to wild <highlight>camping</highlight> on Dartmoor.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在达特穆尔，你可以参加许多活动，从划独木舟到野外露营。

examination_example.sentence: If anyone had told me three years ago that I would be spending most of my weekends <highlight>camping</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果三年前有人告诉我的话，我会把大部分周末都花在露营上。
